window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>It began with a happily ever after. It soon became a nightmare....</p> <p>Norfolk, England, 1816. Joy Horton is resigned to her spinster status. Loathe to pass on her disorder, she refuses to marry and works tirelessly as a skilled seamstress. But when a brooding duke falls madly in love with her, she's unable to resist his persuasive proposal.</p> <p>Honeymooning in London, Joy believes she has everything she's ever wanted...until accusations of murder creep into their lives. When they retreat to the groom's estate and he becomes controlling and obsessive, she fears the mansion walls hide a sinister secret.</p> <p>Can Joy uncover the truth before she's the next victim of a terrifying curse?</p>"; 
